          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Alex Rainer"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Beginners camera course, 3 x 2 hour session over three weeks to master the basics of photography. I was one of 3 participants, nice small group. Alan was very patient, as we all have very different camera to work through setting. Have a much better understanding on my camera and critical setting for getting good images. Would highly recommend the course. HG",
