          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Roz"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am in New Orleans USA and needed a location shoot in Coventry. I emailed several photographers and Alan was the only one that  promptly replied back and discussed the job with me. He not only worked within my budget but gave me quality deliverables, exactly as I needed. Would definitely work with again!",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
