          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Makala Walker"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Beginners photography Course- Alan was wonderful! He gave us incredible tips and insights and explained things in a way that made them make sense. I would definitely recommend this course for anyone wanting to either refresh their basic knowledge is or for complete beginners!",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "datePublished": "2026-03-19",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Google"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Francisca Solis Puello"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Before the session, Alan made sure to understand how I would be using the photos he was going to take and asked about all my requirements to ensure he could offer exactly what I was looking for.  During the session, he gave me several helpful tips to achieve a good photo for the back cover of my first book. I felt comfortable while Alan was taking the photos.  After the photo session, he listened carefully to my feedback and worked on the adjustments until I was satisfied with the final results.  Thank you, Alan, for your patience and the professionalism you bring to your work.",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "datePublished": "2026-03-14",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Google"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Mark Reynolds"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very professional, understanding and above all else gets to the point, knows what he’s talking about and progress in acquiring the required knowledge is quick I’m now convinced I can take my photography skills to where I want want them",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "datePublished": "2026-03-13",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Google"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Jimmy Concannon"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a novice to photography I engaged with Alan to put me in the right direction. From the offset Alan was an inspiration, he has a depth of knowledge which he is willing to pass on. He got me going in the right direction from the first lesson, explained what I should be doing and gave me a better understanding of what to look for whilst taking pictures. During my course I got a good understanding of light, bracketing, settings, the subject, colours, noise, etc. Alan is a very good teacher who makes you feel relaxed. I would highly recommend any novice take a course with Alan it is money very well spent.",
          "reviewRating": {
